    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "1825e716-e13c-4ae3-953c-854a90993ee9",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Windows of Judgment",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128958614100",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5403294c-5390-46ba-a246-4bb6108253c0).Image",
        "Description": "Dartmoor hides its secrets behind stone walls and polished glass, but even the grandest estate cannot escape observation.\nYour five targets—a detective, a photographer, an undertaker, a mansion staff member, and a gardener—each play their part in maintaining the illusion of order.\n\nFrom the windows of the manor, their routines become clear, their paths predictable, and their endings inevitable.\nNo disguises are required, no elaborate accidents necessary—only patience, precision, and the perfect vantage point.\n\nTonight, the estate will learn that judgment often comes from above.",
